{"tid":1292046,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(超限戰) (好文共賞) 2019年，台派不對稱超限戰，開打！","createTime":"2019-07-07T06:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T12:50:40.000Z","uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c4cb4c157d88e2f180da0358cd5914dc3cfbfbfc","tid":1292046,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/875/1*CDMqkhdsY3sSB8pajT9QrA.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F875%2F1%2ACDMqkhdsY3sSB8pajT9QrA.jpeg&h=de228b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這些親匪或者根本就是匪資的媒體，同樣利用台灣民主社會的開放性弱點，公然地為敵國宣傳，相信台灣的淳樸鄉民只要還沒被洗腦的，早就忍無可忍了，於是剿匪學院就要講出第二個戰略目標：困中資<br />\n大家一定會問剿匪學院，這些公司背後有龐大的匪國金流、中客一條龍、買辦產業鏈，我們小小鄉民怎麼跟他們鬥？<br />\n沒錯！剿匪學院不要你去跟他們鬥，各位台派請記得九合一大選怎麼輸掉的，如果你可以動員的資源跟對手不在同一個等級，那麼合法性也好，道德制高點也好，都不能讓你贏得戰爭，台派必須承認一點，就是我們在台灣整體的社會資源中，佔據的份額還遠不如華獨跟老藍藍路。<br />\n於是台派青年必須勇敢站出來，打入華獨跟老藍男陣營裡面，表面上先隱藏自己的政治傾向和認同（社交媒體多設小號），請記得我們尊敬的阿輝伯也在車輪黨隱忍了數十年，才爭取到動用車輪黨資源，反過來拆解車輪黨的機會，因此你越是知道台灣哪些單位可能有匪碟匪資，你就越是要勇敢滲透進去，打入敵人內部，請看下圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/875/1*k-GkHCwi7IdVA5YkeukihA.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F875%2F1%2Ak-GkHCwi7IdVA5YkeukihA.jpeg&h=7ab46c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尤其要設法混進這些單位的資安、財會、業務、公關等要害部門，這是體能不好但是有其他專長的台派，能為台灣抗中做出的最好貢獻，因為匪碟要在台灣建立一套統戰機器，可能需要收買100個台灣人，但是我們只要一個台派打進這些要害部門取得證據，就可以摧毀他們花100個人成本建立的統戰系統，請看王奕凱議員的做法：<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/875/1*MT8T5hwmkvvIXnhEmwfW9g.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F875%2F1%2AMT8T5hwmkvvIXnhEmwfW9g.jpeg&h=fd316336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://medium.com/@laichinan_27202/2019%E5%B9%B4-%E5%8F%B0%E6%B4%BE%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%A8%B1%E8%B6%85%E9%99%90%E6%88%B0-%E9%96%8B%E6%89%93-d668e8cfc53e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40laichinan_27202%2F2019%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%2599%2590%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2589%2593-d668e8cfc53e&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakT1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=fa2a0205\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@laichinan_27202/2019%E5%B9%B4-%E5%8F%B0%E6%B4%BE%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%A8%B1%E8%B6%85%E9%99%90%E6%88%B0-%E9%96%8B%E6%89%93-d668e8cfc53e</a><br />\n<br />\n中國共產黨全方位想吞併香港, 香港係資源上處於絕對劣勢<br />\n所以我地都要出奇招去玩番中共轉頭<br />\n呢篇文提出左三大要點: 習武, 踩建制派場, 打入中資<br />\n非常建議大家慢慢睇哂全文, 多D思考超限戰既方針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393090267c066a9ac098f7ed356e75be71f08224","tid":1292046,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e65ec2388be2eeffea8e932e35cca4b263bd0d8","tid":1292046,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffcc3da509a2b52a9dc9d094c85f931917ecb74","tid":1292046,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c9e1587dfd16a866bf07cfa4b89f2efa20a124","tid":1292046,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884ef1b18820b45524278fddad0d2d1e51913e3f","tid":1292046,"uid":253444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:50:40.000Z","msg":"竟然冇人推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}